reviewText: I was looking forward to this dvd but came away a little disappointed.  The author does really first-rate work, and his models are beautiful, but there was not any real in-depth discussion of methods other than a few fairly simplistic ones. What was there wasn't bad, but was by no means even remotely sufficient to warrant buying this.  Just not the level I was looking for at all.  Although I did enjoy looking at his nice work, I don't feel I gained much of an insight as to how he did it.
